{{'When the maintenance mode is enabled' | uiTranslate}}: <br/><br/>
<ul>
<li>{{'BPM and BDM APIs are not accessible (except BDM installation).' | uiTranslate}}
</li>
<li>{{'Users who are currently logged in, including Administrator users, are automatically redirected to a maintenance page.' | uiTranslate}}
</li>
<li>{{'Users who are filling in forms when the services are paused will lose any information that has not been submitted.' | uiTranslate}}
</li>
<li>{{'All processes are automatically paused.' | uiTranslate}}
</li>
</ul>
